469
00:46:45,000 --> 00:46:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo, mogu vam ja reći.

470
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bude ona, već buboj nju priveli.

471
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bude ona.

472
00:46:50,000 --> 00:46:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad ono veli tata doma, i ja, zdravko, osto suhih rukava, ništa od plesa.

473
00:46:55,000 --> 00:46:57,000
