498
00:48:58,000 --> 00:49:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ste došli u njenu kuću?

499
00:49:00,000 --> 00:49:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Došao sam mijenjati marke.

500
00:49:03,000 --> 00:49:04,000
